{"tid":544076,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為何港女中式婚宴上一定有乳豬全體","createTime":"2018-01-29T07:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T01:30:52.000Z","uid":65328,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"347bd2b8288d01db68aeda2325a4b2217ad83acf","tid":544076,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"疑團：為何中式婚宴上一定有乳豬全體？<br />\n<br />\n解開疑團：古時，男家娶新抱，最重要是希望娶到身家清白的黃花閨女。於洞房花燭夜驗明正身之後，男家就會以乳豬全體大宴親朋，讓全村人知道男家娶得好媳婦。因此，在傅統中國社會，乳豬全體可以說是女性清白之身的認證，對傳統中國女性有著非常重要的意義。<br />\n<br />\n另外，婚宴過後，男家亦會在新娘回門當日送一隻燒豬到女家。燒豬體積大小，顯示男家對新抱的滿意度。當然，燒豬體積越大，就越表示男家對新抱越滿意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那麼為何港女中式婚宴上一定有乳豬全體， 為何女方會要求男家擺酒俾最大份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：中產A0"},{"pid":"85d1c023fbdec8f5a1904b504bd0b19fd8d58076","tid":544076,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3066cee05eefa7a9dba4582c59ab6a882368073c","tid":544076,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85d1c023fbdec8f5a1904b504bd0b19fd8d58076","tid":544076,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:24:36.000Z","msg":"傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"隻豬無左架啦喎"},{"pid":"9b1dd13fd3260e0b89b74a335c51a6ad2f2d6e4c","tid":544076,"uid":99805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"傳統要有既錢,金,禮,乜都要有<br />\n就係無左個處女囉"},{"pid":"8352cc5245bf28cb4fdacf7bacba1549fb4deeda","tid":544076,"uid":120801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/w8n2NRhtjCA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fw8n2NRhtjCA&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=0dacae53\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/w8n2NRhtjCA</a>"},{"pid":"c987aca32e15872f668e94da4b2578ca3655d0ee","tid":54